317
00:17:25,335 --> 00:17:26,503
Ada anak laki-laki?

318
00:17:27,546 --> 00:17:29,339
Kau tampan.

319
00:17:29,423 --> 00:17:32,760
Etnismu apa? Biar kutebak tiga kali.

320
00:17:32,843 --> 00:17:34,970
Tidak, jangan. Ayo.

321
00:17:35,054 --> 00:17:38,682
Pintu ini harus tetap terbuka.

